they'll never take your objective. And he's 100%

32:24.721 --> 32:28.206
right. China wants to come in, just tell them I'm 
going to have to nuke hell out of you, baby. So if you

32:33.430 --> 32:41.397
want to come into this, I'm going to nuke hell out of 
you because I don't have enough ground forces here

32:33.430 --> 32:41.397
to cover you convincingly, and you ought to know 
that. So you get in it, and I'm going to nuke hell out

32:41.917 --> 32:44.800
of you. What do you think they're going to do? 
