do you know? Oh, they monitor you. When you're in 
the clear on the radio, they'll come up on your net,

43:52.121 --> 44:05.682
and they'll call you by your call sign, when you're 
in the clear on the clear net. Did he mention you in

44:05.702 --> 44:07.424
his memoirs? I don't remember. No, I don't know 
whether he did or not. He probably didn't want to

